Usage: speak [OPTIONS] PHRASE

speak - talks back to you
Author: Gregory Vincic

Options
    -n, --dry-run
    -u, --username, $USER : ""
    -r, --role : "user" [user admin]
    -h, --help

Phrases
    askName (default)
    sayHi
        -t, --to : "stranger"
    compliment
        -s, --someone : "John"

Examples
    Greet
        $ speek sayHi -t John
        Hi, John!
